WEBVTT

00:01:29.255 --> 00:01:31.458
into the full chromatic scale:

00:01:31.482 --> 00:01:32.690
the steel pan.

00:01:33.087 --> 00:01:37.471
Playing music now from Beethoven
to Bob Marley to 50 Cent,

00:01:37.495 --> 00:01:41.733
those people literally made
music out of garbage.

00:01:42.754 --> 00:01:45.253
Twelve days before my 20th birthday,

00:01:45.277 --> 00:01:49.148
I was arrested for my role
in a violent robbery attempt

00:01:49.172 --> 00:01:50.384
in lower Manhattan.

00:01:51.001 --> 00:01:53.197
While people were sitting
in a coffee shop,

00:01:54.352 --> 00:01:55.719
four people were shot.

00:01:57.372 --> 00:01:58.699
Two were killed.

00:01:59.684 --> 00:02:01.125
Five of us were arrested.